sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant I as index.js
    participant C as Component
    participant S as Servlet
    participant D as DAO
    participant SE as Session

    U ->> I: action
    I ->> S: AJAX POST /servlet?action=...
    S ->> SE: getAttribute(...)
    SE -->> S: attribute
    S ->> S: resp.getParameter(action)
    S ->> S: internal logic

    S ->> D: saveNewDatabaseDatas()

    S -->> I: response
    I ->> C: render data



